WEBVTT

01:51.310 --> 01:57.530
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.490 --> 02:01.830
[Episode 2]

02:02.190 --> 02:06.530
[Lou Qiyan, Owner of Juyun Pavilion]

02:09.750 --> 02:10.360
Who...

02:11.560 --> 02:12.430
Who is that man?

02:12.950 --> 02:14.060
Double?

02:14.080 --> 02:16.540
Just expected
of the boss of Juyun Pavilion.

02:16.960 --> 02:18.240
Is Young Master Qiyan

02:18.240 --> 02:20.360
also lusting after Miss Hu Die's beauty

02:20.360 --> 02:22.079
and dying to see her in person?

02:22.079 --> 02:24.170
He's just a lecher.

02:24.170 --> 02:26.240
Now, he's trying to acquire Huan'e House.

02:26.240 --> 02:27.770
Who knows what his real purpose is?

02:27.770 --> 02:28.960
So, he is

02:29.490 --> 02:31.760
Lou Qiyan, head of Juyun Pavilion.

02:37.730 --> 02:38.520
Lord Wei,

02:38.840 --> 02:40.010
it was this man who harmed

02:40.010 --> 02:41.930
the businesses in the West Market.

02:41.930 --> 02:43.329
We must not lose to him.

02:44.040 --> 02:45.450
One hundred taels of gold!

02:45.450 --> 02:46.490
Well done!

02:47.329 --> 02:48.790
Two hundred taels of gold.

02:49.560 --> 02:51.420
Two hundred and ten taels of gold!

02:52.290 --> 02:53.820
I thought you'd offer more.

02:54.079 --> 02:55.610
Five hundred taels of gold!

02:56.490 --> 02:58.020
Five hundred taels of gold?

03:01.770 --> 03:03.370
Could you offer a higher bid?

03:03.400 --> 03:03.950
Five...

03:05.010 --> 03:07.330
Five hundred and ten taels of gold!

03:08.170 --> 03:10.100
Today, I'll fight you till the end.

03:12.960 --> 03:14.890
Adding ten gold taels at a time...

03:16.220 --> 03:18.010
Are you here to mess with me?

03:18.040 --> 03:20.240
One thousand two hundred taels of gold!

03:23.329 --> 03:27.329
-One thousand two hundred taels...
--One thousand two hundred taels...

03:27.329 --> 03:29.520
How is he so rich?

03:29.520 --> 03:31.010
I don't think Miss Hu Die and I are

03:31.010 --> 03:32.270
meant to meet up today.

03:33.520 --> 03:34.770
Goodbye, Miss Hu Die.

03:37.520 --> 03:39.450
You are Young Master Qiyan, right?

03:39.730 --> 03:42.400
The fact that you offered
1,200 taels of gold today

03:42.400 --> 03:43.990
for a meeting with Miss Hu Die,

03:43.990 --> 03:45.810
you must have
an important question to ask.

03:45.810 --> 03:47.640
Given that, I should kindly do you a favor

03:47.640 --> 03:48.450
and let you have it.

03:48.450 --> 03:49.640
No, no, no.

03:49.640 --> 03:51.490
We can also have an important question
to ask.

03:51.490 --> 03:54.520
Won't it ache your heart to quit so soon?
Raise the bid, please.

03:54.520 --> 03:55.360
No, it won't.

03:55.400 --> 03:56.660
Just call a higher bid.

03:58.990 --> 04:00.560
How about you offer 1,200 taels of gold

04:00.560 --> 04:02.050
and I pay an extra ten?

04:04.890 --> 04:07.490
I-I don't have that much money.

04:09.770 --> 04:10.490
Alright.

04:10.830 --> 04:13.030
Congratulations, Young Master Qiyan!

04:22.040 --> 04:24.240
For god's sake, you're the Nine Cities'...

04:24.240 --> 04:25.040
Well,

04:25.130 --> 04:27.590
I mean you command
the Nine Cities's Guardian Corps.

04:27.590 --> 04:30.200
How can you let him walk all over us?

04:40.409 --> 04:41.760
The pattern on his collar

04:41.760 --> 04:43.760
seems to be exclusive to the nobles.

04:44.200 --> 04:45.800
Is Juyun Pavilion secretly connected

04:45.800 --> 04:47.330
to the Nine Noble Families?

04:53.760 --> 04:54.680
What?

04:56.080 --> 04:57.850
I'll pay you three taels to do me a favor.

04:57.850 --> 04:58.800
Three taels?

05:00.320 --> 05:03.180
You really think
money can get you everything, huh?

05:03.680 --> 05:04.540
Ten taels then.

05:07.350 --> 05:08.950
Tell me. What favor is it?

05:33.850 --> 05:35.110
What beautiful music.

05:35.400 --> 05:36.400
Beautiful music?

05:37.560 --> 05:38.240
Boss,

05:38.320 --> 05:40.330
aren't you tone-deaf?

06:07.680 --> 06:10.220
This leader of merchants reeks of money.

06:10.250 --> 06:12.780
Why is he suddenly in the mood
for refined art?

06:19.490 --> 06:21.360
I've long heard
that the owner of Huan'e House

06:21.360 --> 06:22.610
is incomparably gorgeous

06:22.610 --> 06:24.210
with excellent erhu skills.

06:24.440 --> 06:26.500
You truly live up to your reputation.

06:27.880 --> 06:28.970
Sir,

06:29.650 --> 06:31.510
have you heard this piece before?

06:31.610 --> 06:32.440
No, never.

06:33.409 --> 06:34.650
Then why would you...

06:35.409 --> 06:38.070
I've never heard it,
but I know the meaning of it.

06:39.440 --> 06:40.640
I can feel...

06:42.680 --> 06:44.210
that it's an ode to vastness

06:45.409 --> 06:46.240
and freedom.

06:49.490 --> 06:50.880
Sir, that's quite

06:51.850 --> 06:53.090
a unique insight.

06:53.760 --> 06:55.560
I must have made a fool of myself.

06:55.610 --> 06:57.210
I just hope you, who's keenly

06:57.360 --> 07:00.160
appreciative of my talent,
aren't disappointed.

07:01.410 --> 07:02.940
Keenly appreciative, huh?

07:04.650 --> 07:05.850
Young Master Qiyan,

07:06.360 --> 07:09.090
I wonder why you went to great lengths
for a chance

07:09.170 --> 07:10.500
to meet me in my boudoir.

07:12.730 --> 07:14.390
You and I both know the reason.

07:14.560 --> 07:16.290
Let's not beat around the bush.

07:16.970 --> 07:19.230
You must've figured out my real purpose,

07:19.490 --> 07:22.320
so you repeatedly turned away
my men from Juyun Pavilion.

07:22.320 --> 07:23.580
You're mistaken, sir.

07:24.490 --> 07:25.680
I'm only running

07:26.050 --> 07:27.530
a small business here.

07:28.070 --> 07:29.480
How could I have expected

07:29.610 --> 07:31.210
that it would catch your eye?

07:32.530 --> 07:33.990
No need for modesty, miss.

07:34.970 --> 07:37.170
Since you don't know much
about Juyun Pavilion,

07:37.170 --> 07:38.370
it's only reasonable

07:38.970 --> 07:40.040
that you feel wary.

07:41.090 --> 07:42.090
Truth to be told,

07:43.320 --> 07:45.120
this time, I came all the way here

07:45.440 --> 07:47.420
to buy out the entire Huan'e House.

07:48.770 --> 07:49.480
You...

07:50.290 --> 07:51.290
You're looking to

07:52.440 --> 07:54.170
acquire Huan'e House?

07:56.800 --> 07:59.530
The tavern business in Ling'an
seems lucrative.

08:00.090 --> 08:02.660
But the interests involved
are tangled and complex.

08:02.660 --> 08:05.800
That has caused countless merchants
to suffer failures.

08:05.800 --> 08:07.930
Nonetheless, your house managed to rise

08:07.930 --> 08:09.530
to the top in just a few years.

08:11.050 --> 08:13.710
There must be an expert
guiding you from behind.

08:14.930 --> 08:16.320
Miss Hu Die, I wonder

08:16.760 --> 08:19.020
if you could introduce me to this person.

08:19.530 --> 08:20.680
I...

08:21.530 --> 08:22.880
Well...

08:25.130 --> 08:26.260
Young Master Qiyan,

08:26.530 --> 08:28.530
please ignore those street rumors.

08:29.200 --> 08:30.200
How about this?

08:30.850 --> 08:32.159
Pay me the deposit

08:32.320 --> 08:34.130
for the Seating Ceremony first.

08:34.320 --> 08:35.850
Then we can have a nice talk.

08:35.929 --> 08:36.929
What do you think?

08:42.059 --> 08:44.730
Girls!

08:44.820 --> 08:47.130
Make sure this young master
is well entertained.

08:47.130 --> 08:48.650
Perhaps when he finds it enjoyable,

08:48.650 --> 08:50.680
he'll come pay for service here every day.

08:50.680 --> 08:51.720
You ladies...

08:51.720 --> 08:53.370
Fancy a fun time, mister?

08:55.370 --> 08:56.560
Mister.

08:58.200 --> 08:59.680
Come have fun with us!

09:09.770 --> 09:11.250
I'll pay you ten taels of gold

09:11.250 --> 09:12.600
to obtain the fabric pattern

09:12.600 --> 09:14.530
from Young Master Qiyan's collar.

09:17.180 --> 09:17.580
Why...

09:17.600 --> 09:18.770
Why do you want that?

09:18.770 --> 09:20.170
Because it looks pretty.

09:20.600 --> 09:22.560
I'll have the Garment Manufacturing Bureau
produce something alike.

09:22.560 --> 09:23.600
As long as...

09:24.200 --> 09:25.410
there's adequate pay,

09:25.410 --> 09:26.810
I'll do all your bidding.

09:28.840 --> 09:29.800
Deal.

09:31.130 --> 09:32.460
Consider the task done.

09:37.050 --> 09:38.520
What's going on?

09:44.730 --> 09:46.390
You really are not Miss Hu Die.

09:52.370 --> 09:54.170
Greetings, Young Master Qiyan.

09:55.080 --> 09:57.030
How about

09:57.480 --> 09:59.010
we meet again another time?

09:59.370 --> 10:00.900
Until the next time we weet!

10:01.370 --> 10:02.130
Guards!

10:03.340 --> 10:04.580
-Boss.
-Go get her!

10:04.680 --> 10:05.400
-Yes.
-Yes.

10:08.870 --> 10:10.160
Mr. Lou.

10:16.820 --> 10:19.420
[Owner of Huan'e House, Miss Hu Die]

10:20.270 --> 10:21.380
Miss Hu Die.

10:38.270 --> 10:40.460
Lord Wei! Lord Wei!

10:46.200 --> 10:47.150
How did I do?

10:47.600 --> 10:48.720
Impressive, huh?

10:50.080 --> 10:51.540
You really are something.

10:52.480 --> 10:53.320
Stop there!

10:56.370 --> 10:57.130
What is this about?

10:57.130 --> 10:57.800
Hurry, hurry!

10:57.800 --> 10:59.130
Run!

10:59.130 --> 11:00.050
Get a move on!

11:01.480 --> 11:02.080
Halt!

11:02.610 --> 11:04.090
You lot, go catch them!

11:04.120 --> 11:04.780
-Yes!
-Yes!

11:42.180 --> 11:43.610
How satisfying.

11:55.850 --> 11:58.160
Turn Ling'an upside down if necessary.

11:58.480 --> 12:00.170
Just find those people for me.

12:00.290 --> 12:01.200
-Yes.
-Yes.

12:05.260 --> 12:13.000
[Juyun Pavilion]

12:32.440 --> 12:34.570
You must be tired from all the studying

12:35.200 --> 12:36.800
at the Directorate of Education today.

12:36.090 --> 12:39.100
[Zheng Shi, the second young master
of the Zheng family]

12:38.320 --> 12:40.920
You should have some pig brains
for nutrition.

12:42.630 --> 12:44.160
These are spicy pig brains.

12:44.170 --> 12:45.250
These were cooked with garlic.

12:45.250 --> 12:47.320
These were braised with sauce.

12:48.130 --> 12:49.180
I had these dishes

12:49.720 --> 12:52.200
prepared especially for you.

12:53.890 --> 12:55.290
Thank you, Grandfather.

12:55.480 --> 12:56.930
But, Grandfather,

12:57.320 --> 12:59.590
I already learned
what the Directorate of Education

12:59.590 --> 13:01.520
is teaching now back in Jingcheng.

13:02.050 --> 13:03.290
The old tutors here

13:03.770 --> 13:05.300
are not as good as expected.

13:06.760 --> 13:08.310
Mind your language.

13:08.800 --> 13:09.630
Master!

13:13.650 --> 13:15.840
Young Master Shi, you're back.

13:15.840 --> 13:17.130
What's that gibberish?

13:17.130 --> 13:18.650
Shi just came back from the directorate.

13:18.650 --> 13:20.250
He's already exhausted.

13:21.040 --> 13:22.300
You're right, Master.

13:23.840 --> 13:24.970
Those old tutors...

13:25.480 --> 13:27.140
Have they really let you down?

13:30.650 --> 13:31.530
Zheng Yi,

13:31.960 --> 13:34.560
inform the Directorate of Education
tomorrow

13:35.010 --> 13:36.140
of getting Zheng Shi

13:37.080 --> 13:37.890
a new

13:38.370 --> 13:39.530
primary tutor.

13:41.560 --> 13:43.180
Not just anyone can teach

13:43.650 --> 13:45.800
the children of us Zheng family.

13:46.600 --> 13:47.290
Got it.

13:50.530 --> 13:51.330
Grandfather.

13:52.050 --> 13:53.010
I'm full.

13:53.010 --> 13:54.480
I'll go study in my room then.

13:54.480 --> 13:56.530
Would you like a cup of hot tea?

13:57.770 --> 13:59.800
Which flavor do you like?

14:00.680 --> 14:03.280
I'll have the kitchen
make it for you tomorrow.

14:04.290 --> 14:05.410
Don't bother!

14:06.170 --> 14:09.370
I'll have the staff serve
all the flavors again tomorrow.

14:10.060 --> 14:11.320
Thanks, Grandfather.

14:33.170 --> 14:34.430
What are you laughing at?

14:34.430 --> 14:35.240
Master,

14:35.730 --> 14:37.990
you're truly doting on Young Master Shi.

14:38.080 --> 14:39.510
Of course.

14:39.930 --> 14:41.200
Among all my grandsons,

14:41.200 --> 14:42.600
he resembles me the most.

14:44.860 --> 14:46.130
Come on, slowly.

14:46.150 --> 14:46.960
Drink up!

14:48.530 --> 14:49.370
Gao Ran,

14:49.370 --> 14:52.360
it's too late for him and me to go home.

14:52.390 --> 14:53.470
So, tonight,

14:53.490 --> 14:55.180
he and I will both sleep here.

14:55.220 --> 14:55.820
Oh, right.

14:56.200 --> 14:58.810
This is Lord Wei.

15:01.580 --> 15:03.010
He's utterly brilliant.

15:06.320 --> 15:07.170
Let me walk you to your room.

15:07.170 --> 15:07.720
No need!

15:08.130 --> 15:08.530
Come this way.

15:08.530 --> 15:09.860
I don't need help at all!

15:10.010 --> 15:11.200
See you tomorrow.

15:11.800 --> 15:13.940
-Take care then.
-I can go back to my room on my own.

15:13.940 --> 15:14.910
Where to go?

15:15.930 --> 15:17.090
This way, come on.

15:17.120 --> 15:18.550
Back to my room...

15:20.210 --> 15:21.900
Have we met somewhere before?

15:22.480 --> 15:24.410
How come you look so familiar to me?

15:25.120 --> 15:26.620
I work in the Guardian Corps now.

15:26.620 --> 15:28.140
So I often show up in the Qi Residence.

15:28.140 --> 15:30.200
It's no surprise that you've seen me.

15:31.700 --> 15:33.640
Today, new books arrived
at Qilin Pavilion.

15:33.640 --> 15:35.680
I don't think
Lord Fan Qi will come back tonight.

15:35.680 --> 15:37.680
So you can stay the night in his room.

15:38.840 --> 15:40.170
No need to walk me there.

16:41.720 --> 16:43.530
Why is my entire body aching?

16:45.200 --> 16:46.390
My head hurts.

16:47.200 --> 16:48.470
Every part hurts.

17:07.960 --> 17:08.760
Lord Wei!

17:10.460 --> 17:12.220
Why are you up so early?

17:15.000 --> 17:15.849
Come over.

17:22.569 --> 17:23.630
What's the matter?

17:23.810 --> 17:24.609
Let me ask you.

17:25.410 --> 17:27.569
How long has that bedroom been vacant?

17:27.930 --> 17:29.240
Last night, the bed that I,

17:29.240 --> 17:30.170
the honorable...

17:30.170 --> 17:31.930
slept in gave me a terrible backache.

17:31.930 --> 17:32.720
The Fan family is wealthy.

17:32.720 --> 17:35.050
Can't you pay a little sum
to have it fixed?

17:38.660 --> 17:42.590
Your judgement's really clouded
by the high walls of the Qi Residence.

17:42.760 --> 17:44.480
There's something
you don't know, Lord Wei.

17:44.480 --> 17:45.610
For commoners,

17:45.610 --> 17:47.070
living in a house like this

17:47.380 --> 17:48.560
is already a luxury.

17:50.810 --> 17:52.470
Then I have another question.

17:52.810 --> 17:55.160
Why is this tree of yours so withered?

17:58.370 --> 17:59.480
You mean this tree?

18:00.890 --> 18:01.970
Well, it used to be

18:02.680 --> 18:04.350
towering and majestic.

18:05.480 --> 18:06.910
Look at the bells on it.

18:07.680 --> 18:09.850
When I grew taller every year,

18:10.280 --> 18:12.610
my mother would hang a bell there
as a mark.

18:14.200 --> 18:15.280
Unfortunately,

18:16.330 --> 18:17.890
she is no longer around.

18:23.890 --> 18:25.130
Lord Wei,

18:25.480 --> 18:27.930
you've never seen anyone
with extreme hunger,

18:27.930 --> 18:29.150
have you?

18:31.890 --> 18:33.020
Those usually

18:33.330 --> 18:34.930
kind and amiable old ladies,

18:36.370 --> 18:37.500
and the men and women

18:37.890 --> 18:39.620
who used to lovingly pat my head

18:40.000 --> 18:41.890
and call me "young miss"

18:43.810 --> 18:45.810
would fight fiercely till they bled

18:46.440 --> 18:48.230
just for a leaf

18:49.610 --> 18:51.520
or even a sour steamed bun.

18:53.240 --> 18:55.500
Every day when my mother opened the door,

18:55.610 --> 18:58.010
she could see starving people everywhere.

18:58.440 --> 18:59.700
Living souls perished

18:59.890 --> 19:01.690
from hunger in every single day.

19:03.090 --> 19:04.820
They died right before my eyes.

19:06.810 --> 19:08.570
It was also the time

19:09.240 --> 19:10.700
when my mother passed away

19:11.440 --> 19:12.720
for overexertion.

19:15.480 --> 19:16.480
My father said

19:17.370 --> 19:18.520
my mother's death

19:19.610 --> 19:21.850
was exactly caused

19:23.200 --> 19:24.760
by such cruel reality.

19:30.930 --> 19:32.530
Under these circumstances,

19:33.000 --> 19:34.040
what can I do?

19:36.440 --> 19:37.660
In the Nine Cities,

19:38.930 --> 19:40.680
if I am to do something for the people

19:40.680 --> 19:42.140
or to make a contribution,

19:42.440 --> 19:43.890
how do I make it happen

19:44.810 --> 19:46.390
without an official post?

19:48.240 --> 19:49.240
Your Excellency,

19:49.520 --> 19:51.230
have you never thought about

19:51.250 --> 19:52.850
changing the future of the Nine Cities

19:52.850 --> 19:54.120
and enabling the people here to live

19:54.120 --> 19:56.780
a life without worries
about food and clothing?

20:05.450 --> 20:07.380
When did you know I am the governor?

20:09.370 --> 20:11.770
Deceiving a superior is a capital offense.

20:13.090 --> 20:14.740
I knew it from the very beginning.

20:14.740 --> 20:15.870
The very beginning?

20:18.850 --> 20:20.240
So you already figured out my identity

20:20.240 --> 20:22.100
when we were in the Phoenix Woods?

20:26.680 --> 20:28.880
I knew nothing could restrain my charm.

20:31.500 --> 20:32.250
You...

20:35.650 --> 20:37.380
I bet the saplings planted here

20:37.440 --> 20:39.090
can't grow well due to failure

20:39.090 --> 20:40.290
to absorb nutrition.

20:41.720 --> 20:43.320
If they are moved elsewhere,

20:43.570 --> 20:45.100
I am sure they will flourish

20:45.130 --> 20:46.060
and bloom again.

21:09.470 --> 21:10.870
I hope the Nine Cities

21:11.130 --> 21:12.870
can grow prosperous and grand

21:13.330 --> 21:14.930
like this sapling

21:15.370 --> 21:16.630
to shelter the people.

21:18.330 --> 21:19.650
Maybe one day,

21:20.440 --> 21:22.700
I can also contribute to the Nine Cities.

21:24.760 --> 21:27.690
What if every citizen
could take the official exams?

21:30.680 --> 21:32.620
-What did you say?
-I was just kidding.

21:32.620 --> 21:34.000
Look how shocked you are.

21:34.000 --> 21:35.280
You were not kidding.

21:35.280 --> 21:36.680
I heard what you said.

21:36.680 --> 21:37.650
Did you mean it?

21:40.000 --> 21:41.600
I'll make one more wish then.

21:41.930 --> 21:45.080
I hope all the people in the Nine Cities

21:45.480 --> 21:47.720
can realize their lofty ambitions.

21:57.440 --> 22:00.430
[Huan'e House]

22:03.650 --> 22:05.280
These are the recent accounts.

22:05.280 --> 22:08.140
Yesterday's Seating Ceremony
is recorded as well.

22:09.200 --> 22:09.960
Hu Die,

22:11.240 --> 22:13.650
during all these years,
by trading information,

22:13.650 --> 22:15.760
Huan'e House has not only
raked in big money,

22:15.760 --> 22:18.330
but also collected
many secrets of the nobles.

22:18.330 --> 22:19.930
Thank you for your hard work.

22:20.040 --> 22:21.250
I'm just doing my job.

22:21.810 --> 22:22.440
To be honest,

22:22.440 --> 22:25.120
I think only Your Excellency would inflate

22:25.370 --> 22:27.700
your own value in your own establishment.

22:29.090 --> 22:30.350
If I were truly greedy,

22:30.730 --> 22:32.860
I could've earned much more than this.

22:33.550 --> 22:36.280
Knowing when to stop
allows one to remain hidden.

22:37.480 --> 22:39.230
Speaking of remaining hidden,

22:40.590 --> 22:43.520
nobody can do it better
than Your Excellency, right?

22:45.040 --> 22:48.240
Last night, Your Excellency slept
at Her Ladyship's place.

22:48.240 --> 22:50.130
It was because of the note
I passed onto you,

22:50.130 --> 22:52.260
the one about the Dark Wolf, wasn't it?

22:56.440 --> 22:57.810
This was written

22:57.810 --> 22:59.810
by the Dark Wolf leader 13 years ago.

23:00.280 --> 23:01.550
Please take a look.

23:09.040 --> 23:10.630
How did you get this letter?

23:10.660 --> 23:13.230
By chance, from the Dark Wolf remnants.

23:14.170 --> 23:15.970
But due to my incompetence,

23:16.280 --> 23:18.610
the Dark Wolf leader
and the Dark Wolf Seal

23:19.200 --> 23:20.730
are still unaccounted for.

23:23.300 --> 23:26.280
The Dark Wolf organization was founded
by my late father.

23:26.280 --> 23:28.280
It only answers to its real ruler,

23:29.150 --> 23:31.480
namely the one holding the Dark Wolf Seal.

23:31.800 --> 23:33.910
My late father used to keep this item.

23:35.100 --> 23:36.960
But after the war for succession,

23:37.370 --> 23:38.720
this seal disappeared.

23:40.130 --> 23:41.810
Even if I am to take power,

23:42.540 --> 23:44.340
I won't have a legitimate reason

23:44.520 --> 23:45.980
to do so without this seal.

23:46.440 --> 23:48.730
I understand. I'll try my best to find it.

23:49.120 --> 23:50.840
Hold off on this for now.

23:53.610 --> 23:54.960
It is no easy task.

23:55.650 --> 23:57.570
But about Her Ladyship...

24:06.620 --> 24:07.750
This woman...

24:08.690 --> 24:10.320
It's not a bad idea to use her.

24:12.200 --> 24:15.200
At first, I only thought
she had a complex background.

24:15.200 --> 24:16.660
Lord Lyu picked her for me,

24:17.160 --> 24:19.520
and the Three Excellencies gave her dowry.

24:19.520 --> 24:21.920
I can't believe
she'd put on all that stuff.

24:22.330 --> 24:23.280
It somehow confuses me

24:23.280 --> 24:24.850
as to what she's truly up to.

24:27.040 --> 24:27.810
By the way,

24:28.280 --> 24:30.410
I asked you to shut down the shops
with a rogue mark.

24:30.410 --> 24:31.520
Have you done it?

24:37.300 --> 24:38.540
What's this about?

24:38.560 --> 24:40.320
Who shut it down?

24:38.690 --> 24:41.440
[Baiyu Hall]

24:55.740 --> 24:57.580
What on earth is going on?

25:05.650 --> 25:06.620
Is the governor

25:07.890 --> 25:09.950
playing dumb with us?

25:38.580 --> 25:40.440
You draw so beautifully, My Lady.

25:44.760 --> 25:45.720
Good, isn't it?

25:47.130 --> 25:47.810
This is

25:47.810 --> 25:50.610
the pattern
of the Splendid Mountains and Rivers.

25:56.650 --> 25:57.810
Suyin,

25:57.810 --> 25:59.210
what are you drawing?

26:00.000 --> 26:01.170
Take a guess.

26:02.930 --> 26:04.520
I guess...

26:09.960 --> 26:11.640
you're drawing a little lion.

26:11.660 --> 26:12.920
It looks quite like it.

26:16.440 --> 26:17.160
My Lady,

26:17.850 --> 26:19.680
this is a sunflower.

26:20.640 --> 26:22.810
A s-sunflower?

26:27.410 --> 26:29.450
What a unique sunflower.

26:30.560 --> 26:31.830
Keep working on it then.

26:31.830 --> 26:32.620
Just go on.

26:33.110 --> 26:34.140
It's good.

26:35.960 --> 26:37.890
Your drawing is really lifelike, My Lady.

26:37.890 --> 26:39.570
Is it a gift for His Excellency?

26:39.570 --> 26:40.890
What a terrific painting it is.

26:40.890 --> 26:42.950
I'm sure His Excellency will like it.

26:45.170 --> 26:46.440
Now that I think of it,

26:48.050 --> 26:49.910
it might not be necessarily true.

26:51.170 --> 26:53.360
What do you mean by that, My Lady?

26:55.680 --> 26:56.960
Anyway,

26:57.370 --> 26:58.650
the governor is probably

26:58.650 --> 27:00.480
not what he appears to be.

27:10.850 --> 27:12.650
You should go to bed early, My Lady.

27:12.650 --> 27:15.580
I don't think
His Excellency will come here tonight.

27:18.850 --> 27:21.700
His Excellency has arrived!

27:25.120 --> 27:27.600
W-Why would the governor

27:27.620 --> 27:29.790
c-come here at this hour of the night?

27:42.410 --> 27:44.070
Greetings, Your Excellency.

27:44.230 --> 27:46.160
If you have nothing else to do here,

27:46.200 --> 27:47.280
just leave.

27:59.330 --> 28:00.890
It's already late at night.

28:01.370 --> 28:03.100
Why are you still up, Governor?

28:19.090 --> 28:20.240
These are...

28:20.650 --> 28:21.570
roses?

28:23.170 --> 28:25.680
I know your mother's name was Qiangwei,
which means roses.

28:25.680 --> 28:26.780
I happened to see

28:26.960 --> 28:29.130
these beautiful blossoms on my way here.

28:29.130 --> 28:30.660
Come on, take them as a gift.

28:32.170 --> 28:33.520
How thoughtful of you, Governor.

28:33.520 --> 28:34.520
I'm afraid...

28:34.520 --> 28:35.780
I don't deserve these.

28:37.760 --> 28:39.290
Just take them as I told you.

28:39.650 --> 28:41.050
Don't stand on ceremony.

28:42.960 --> 28:43.730
Governor,

28:44.090 --> 28:45.570
there is a scratch on your finger.

28:45.570 --> 28:47.570
Please come in and let me bandage it.

28:48.760 --> 28:50.620
This minor scratch is no big deal.

28:50.810 --> 28:52.210
If there's nothing else,

28:52.810 --> 28:54.410
I'd like to go back to my room.

28:55.410 --> 28:56.380
Just come on in!

28:59.550 --> 29:00.250
Sure.

29:15.650 --> 29:17.550
Your hand is just like Gao Ran's.

29:20.810 --> 29:21.490
Gao Ran?

29:22.960 --> 29:25.160
You mean the one you see as your brother?

29:25.650 --> 29:28.480
Has he been practicing sword skills
since childhood too?

29:28.480 --> 29:29.200
Yes.

29:29.680 --> 29:30.600
Anyway,

29:31.000 --> 29:33.440
Gao Ran has exceptional martial skills.

29:34.440 --> 29:35.240
Alright.

29:35.240 --> 29:36.100
It's bandaged.

29:36.520 --> 29:37.650
Governor, remember

29:37.830 --> 29:39.530
not to get this finger wet.

29:40.940 --> 29:42.140
It's just a minor cut.

29:43.330 --> 29:44.290
Thank you.

29:47.520 --> 29:48.170
By the way,

29:49.520 --> 29:50.750
from now on, please

29:51.240 --> 29:52.500
just call me by my name.

29:54.680 --> 29:55.480
But...

29:55.810 --> 29:57.000
wouldn't that be

29:57.000 --> 29:58.210
inappropriate?

29:58.650 --> 30:00.450
What's inappropriate about it?

30:00.650 --> 30:02.270
You call Gao Ran by his name.

30:02.930 --> 30:04.530
Why not call me by my name too?

30:06.480 --> 30:07.720
What should I call you then?

30:07.720 --> 30:08.570
"Qi Zheng."

30:09.040 --> 30:09.790
"Qi Zheng"?

30:10.570 --> 30:11.850
You'll call me Qi Zheng,

30:11.850 --> 30:13.130
and I'll call you Fan Yun.

30:13.130 --> 30:14.530
It feels closer this way.

30:16.680 --> 30:17.940
Fine then.

30:18.480 --> 30:20.220
You're the governor after all.

30:21.570 --> 30:22.170
Qi Zheng.

30:24.960 --> 30:25.760
Fan Yun.

30:27.480 --> 30:28.440
Qi Zheng.

30:28.440 --> 30:29.200
Fan Yun.

30:29.610 --> 30:30.370
Qi Zheng.

30:31.170 --> 30:31.960
Fan Yun.

30:43.810 --> 30:44.490
Fan Yun.

30:45.510 --> 30:47.990
Why are roses covered in thorns?

30:51.370 --> 30:53.200
Governor, have you never heard

30:53.200 --> 30:54.890
the story of Princess Rose?

30:55.810 --> 30:57.040
Princess Rose?

30:58.410 --> 30:59.940
I've never heard her story.

31:00.410 --> 31:01.680
Tell me about it then.

31:05.520 --> 31:08.440
When are you going to stop playing dumb?

31:09.040 --> 31:10.500
What exactly are you up to?

31:12.960 --> 31:13.700
Governor,

31:13.920 --> 31:16.530
the night is growing late.

31:16.650 --> 31:17.680
How about we continue tomorrow?

31:17.680 --> 31:18.740
It doesn't matter.

31:19.720 --> 31:21.230
I just love hearing stories.

31:21.230 --> 31:23.160
I'll be gone after this one's told.

31:26.060 --> 31:27.310
Fine.

32:20.440 --> 32:21.440
I-I-I...

32:23.600 --> 32:25.410
I put a pillow in the middle of the bed.

32:25.410 --> 32:27.010
How did it end up being there?

32:27.670 --> 32:28.620
I... This...

32:29.850 --> 32:31.330
I haven't complained about you yet.

32:31.330 --> 32:32.240
How could you fall asleep here

32:32.240 --> 32:33.700
without cause last night?

32:34.610 --> 32:35.610
-You...
-Fan Yun,

32:36.060 --> 32:38.190
do you have a secret crush on me or what?

32:39.590 --> 32:41.590
I... h-have a crush on...

32:43.330 --> 32:44.760
How could you, Qi Zheng?

32:44.760 --> 32:46.360
You slept in my bed,

32:46.570 --> 32:48.960
yet you accuse me
of having a crush on you.

32:50.820 --> 32:52.220
No, this won't do.

32:52.330 --> 32:53.380
From today on,

32:53.760 --> 32:55.410
you must take responsibility for me.

32:55.410 --> 32:56.900
Qi Zheng...

32:57.170 --> 32:58.500
You did that on purpose!

32:58.890 --> 33:00.090
Get out!

33:12.410 --> 33:13.440
Governor?

33:15.520 --> 33:16.340
Look,

33:16.710 --> 33:18.250
we fell asleep last night, right?

33:18.250 --> 33:20.380
You didn't finish telling that story.

33:20.480 --> 33:21.960
I have no story to tell.

33:23.010 --> 33:24.010
Yes, yes, you do.

33:24.030 --> 33:24.860
I'm so eager.

33:24.890 --> 33:25.520
Let's pick up where we left off.

33:25.520 --> 33:27.450
I-I don't have any stories to tell!

33:29.370 --> 33:32.100
I swear I won't tell another story
in my lifetime.

33:32.440 --> 33:33.410
Governor,

33:33.410 --> 33:35.410
I really don't have a story to tell.

33:35.760 --> 33:37.360
-Hurry.
-What are you doing?

33:39.570 --> 33:42.170
-Quick!
-What's this for, Governor?

33:42.340 --> 33:42.860
You...

33:49.090 --> 33:49.570
You...

33:49.960 --> 33:52.070
Are you trying to pull stunts again?

33:54.930 --> 33:55.820
What...

33:55.850 --> 33:57.370
exactly are you doing?

33:59.760 --> 34:00.910
Outside. Outside!

34:09.409 --> 34:10.440
Someone is outside?

34:10.440 --> 34:11.040
Yes.

34:11.040 --> 34:11.850
Hurry.

34:11.850 --> 34:13.050
Help me shake the bed.

34:18.120 --> 34:19.880
[This marks the second time
Her Ladyship slept with His Excellency]

34:29.110 --> 34:30.800
You're being followed again?

34:30.820 --> 34:32.010
Please do me a favor.

34:50.090 --> 34:52.440
[This marks the third time
Her Ladyship slept with His Excellency]

35:06.900 --> 35:09.500
[This marks the fourth time
Her Ladyship slept with His Excellency]

35:24.470 --> 35:27.420
[This marks the... time
Her Ladyship slept with His Excellency]

35:27.500 --> 35:29.370
[Huiyun Pavilion]

35:40.080 --> 35:41.810
How come His Excellency is already

35:41.810 --> 35:43.600
so drowsy just after the morning meeting?

35:43.600 --> 35:46.800
His Excellency seems
to have been resting poorly lately.

35:48.850 --> 35:50.770
T-Then...

35:51.770 --> 35:53.900
-Your Excellency.
-Your Excellency.

35:55.150 --> 35:57.280
-Your Excellency.
-Your Excellency.

36:03.250 --> 36:04.850
Your Excellency, do you know

36:05.440 --> 36:07.250
the treasury is running low?

36:08.810 --> 36:09.960
The treasury?

36:11.930 --> 36:13.000
Did

36:13.000 --> 36:15.800
the Commerce Ministry
not manage the budget well?

36:16.250 --> 36:19.050
This has nothing to do
with the Commerce Ministry.

36:19.520 --> 36:21.120
Since the beginning of this year,

36:21.120 --> 36:22.180
all the Nine Cities

36:22.520 --> 36:23.920
haven't been peaceful.

36:24.730 --> 36:26.890
Multiple areas have been struck
by disasters.

36:26.890 --> 36:28.040
People

36:28.040 --> 36:30.370
failed to pay taxes on time.

36:30.690 --> 36:31.450
This is what

36:31.690 --> 36:34.900
caused the current predicament.

36:38.250 --> 36:39.220
Then, Mr. Zheng,

36:39.640 --> 36:40.950
do you have a solution?

36:42.930 --> 36:44.690
After careful thinking,

36:45.440 --> 36:47.170
I suppose the imminent concern

36:47.440 --> 36:49.570
can only be addressed by higher taxes.

36:50.560 --> 36:53.910
I have drafted a proposal
for raising taxes.

36:54.450 --> 36:56.650
Read it, and Your Excellency will know.

37:03.000 --> 37:04.360
Raising taxes, huh?

37:06.760 --> 37:08.690
It's definitely not going to work.

37:11.040 --> 37:12.890
People can't afford to pay taxes as it is.

37:12.890 --> 37:14.440
Now, you're even proposing an increase.

37:14.440 --> 37:16.640
People will struggle more, won't they?

37:17.120 --> 37:20.370
What gives you that thought,
Your Excellency?

37:24.040 --> 37:25.030
My wife.

37:25.620 --> 37:27.520
Speaking of which,
I owe the three of you many thanks,

37:27.520 --> 37:29.050
for bringing her to my life.

37:29.960 --> 37:30.930
I'm grateful

37:30.930 --> 37:32.890
that she took me out to see people's lives

37:32.890 --> 37:35.220
and told me so much about their suffering.

37:35.250 --> 37:38.050
I really cannot impose higher taxes
on the people.

37:42.740 --> 37:44.260
In my opinion,

37:45.560 --> 37:47.020
it's time to take reforms.

37:47.560 --> 37:49.760
As for whether to raise the taxes or not,

37:49.820 --> 37:51.480
we need further discussions.

38:00.210 --> 38:02.160
I beg to differ, My Lord.

38:03.520 --> 38:05.380
What do you think is wrong with it?

38:06.440 --> 38:08.420
Is it wrong or not?

38:08.690 --> 38:10.550
-Don't chime in.
-Don't chime in.

38:14.160 --> 38:16.290
Women can't participate in politics.

38:16.690 --> 38:17.600
Doesn't

38:17.600 --> 38:19.000
Her Ladyship know that?

38:19.930 --> 38:22.520
I don't think
she's participating in politics.

38:22.520 --> 38:24.100
Is she or is she not?

38:25.370 --> 38:26.100
She's not.

38:36.370 --> 38:38.210
Do you agree with the nonsense

38:38.210 --> 38:39.440
that the governor said?

38:39.440 --> 38:40.590
Of course I agree.

38:40.670 --> 38:43.400
There's no need to hide things
between you and me.

38:44.440 --> 38:46.180
The treasury is depleted.

38:46.960 --> 38:48.040
What other solutions are there

38:48.040 --> 38:49.830
apart from increasing taxes?

38:50.810 --> 38:52.580
His Excellency is stalling.

38:53.480 --> 38:55.330
And that talk about reforms!

38:55.810 --> 38:58.140
Is he trying to turn the world
upside down?

39:00.770 --> 39:02.180
That aside, look

39:02.540 --> 39:04.230
what a woman you got him.

39:04.690 --> 39:06.490
She has bewitched the governor.

39:07.410 --> 39:09.630
And you are the one to blame!

39:10.810 --> 39:12.210
Actually, I think

39:12.960 --> 39:14.440
I picked the right woman.

39:42.960 --> 39:44.600
Please stop looking, My Lady.

39:44.600 --> 39:46.800
You would deem my embroidery terrible.

39:47.130 --> 39:48.320
Who said that?

39:48.340 --> 39:49.850
You're doing a great job at it.

39:49.850 --> 39:52.130
Look at the duckling
you're working on this time.

39:52.130 --> 39:53.460
Such a cute expression.

39:56.150 --> 39:57.000
My Lady,

39:57.370 --> 39:58.780
this is a mandarin duck.

39:59.850 --> 40:00.780
A mandarin duck?

40:02.820 --> 40:03.480
You mean...

40:04.030 --> 40:05.360
this is a mandarin duck?

40:08.640 --> 40:10.040
I guessed it wrong again.

40:13.330 --> 40:14.450
Well, you're right.

40:14.450 --> 40:15.680
This is exactly a mandarin duck.

40:15.680 --> 40:17.180
How beautifully embroidered.

40:17.180 --> 40:19.810
"The mandarin ducks fly together;
Catch them as a pair."

40:19.810 --> 40:21.410
It's a lovely mandarin duck.

40:22.820 --> 40:25.000
My Lady, I know
you're trying to comfort me.

40:25.000 --> 40:26.560
I don't have much talent

40:26.560 --> 40:28.370
in needlework.

40:29.690 --> 40:30.890
Wait, Suyin.

40:31.210 --> 40:32.440
You said...

40:32.670 --> 40:34.460
this is a mandarin duck.

40:36.890 --> 40:39.140
It's said
that words are to convey meaning.

40:39.140 --> 40:41.000
Embroidery works in the same way.

40:41.080 --> 40:42.520
Does it mean...

40:42.690 --> 40:44.120
you're in love

40:44.520 --> 40:45.720
with someone, Suyin?

40:48.560 --> 40:49.210
No.

40:49.210 --> 40:51.120
Don't talk nonsense, My Lady.

40:52.440 --> 40:53.800
No wonder I've always seen you

40:53.800 --> 40:56.060
writing letters in your room these days.

40:56.100 --> 40:58.430
It turns out they're for someone you love.

40:59.380 --> 41:00.540
I remember you are

41:00.570 --> 41:01.740
from Jingcheng.

41:01.910 --> 41:02.770
What about him?

41:02.930 --> 41:04.390
Is he also from Jingcheng?

41:05.930 --> 41:07.330
No, this is

41:07.600 --> 41:09.440
not what you think it is, My Lady.

41:12.790 --> 41:14.490
What's there to be shy about?

41:15.050 --> 41:16.580
Throughout the ages,

41:16.600 --> 41:18.560
nothing moves the heart more than love.

41:18.560 --> 41:20.500
Women's passion is particularly powerful.

41:20.500 --> 41:21.960
If you truly like someone,

41:21.960 --> 41:23.620
then be brave and say it aloud.

41:24.930 --> 41:26.660
My Lady, do you really think so?

41:29.410 --> 41:31.290
Then don't just be a judge

41:31.290 --> 41:32.290
on someone else's affairs.

41:32.290 --> 41:35.550
It's time you directed your attention
to your own matters.

41:36.290 --> 41:37.730
My own matters?

41:37.850 --> 41:38.850
What matters?

41:39.770 --> 41:41.480
Why does it seem like you don't care about

41:41.480 --> 41:42.960
the governor's birthday at all?

41:42.960 --> 41:44.600
Those in the Internal Affairs Department
told me

41:44.600 --> 41:46.210
they've been waiting for your reply

41:46.210 --> 41:48.940
about the menu
for this year's birthday banquet.

41:51.160 --> 41:52.520
You mean...

41:52.850 --> 41:54.300
the mayor's birthday is approaching?
